### Create a new game
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-alice",
  "playerName": "Alice",
  "gameName": "Alice's Awesome Game",
  "options": {
    "maxPlayers": 6,
    "minPlayers": 2,
    "allowSpectators": true,
    "isPrivate": false,
    "allowedCategories": ["Reaction", "Choice"]
  }
}

###

### Get game details by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}

###

### Get game details by game code
GET http://localhost:5000/api/games/by-code/{{gameCode}}

###

### Join a game by ID
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-bob",
  "playerName": "Bob"
}

###

### Join a game by game code
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/join-by-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameCode": "ABC123",
  "playerId": "player-charlie",
  "playerName": "Charlie"
}

###

### Start the game (only game master can do this)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-alice"
}

###

### Get current round information
GET http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/current-round

###

### Submit meme text for a player
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/submit-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-alice",
  "textEntries": {
    "top": "When you see a new meme template",
    "bottom": "Time to make it funny!"
  }
}

###

### Submit another player's meme text
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/submit-text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-bob",
  "textEntries": {
    "top": "Me trying to think of funny text",
    "bottom": "My brain: *empty*"
  }
}

###

### Submit score for another player's meme
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/submit-score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-alice",
  "targetPlayerId": "player-bob", 
  "score": 4
}

###

### Submit score from Bob to Alice
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/submit-score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-bob",
  "targetPlayerId": "player-alice",
  "score": 5
}

###

### Get current scores
GET http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/scores

###

### Leave the game
POST http://localhost:5000/api/games/{{gameId}}/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-charlie"
}

###

### Get available games
GET http://localhost:5000/api/games
